Class FilterManager

java.lang.Object
ch.supsi.business.filter.FilterManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
FilterPipelineInterface
public class FilterManager extends Object implements FilterPipelineInterface
Manages a chain of filters applied to an image. Implements the Singleton pattern to ensure a single instance is used throughout the application. Filters are organized in a chain structure and can be executed sequentially on an image.
